item.title: Pushing Delta 3200
item.description: Unless you’re interested in reading why I like fast film, you can skip to this section for how I actually develop it. item.title: My First Post
item.description: Yeah I might actually use this to write about things. (2022-02-03): I’ve got so many half-finished drafts that have just been sitting there, neatly tucked away in their own little branches. Maybe I was just never destined to write like this.
